    "long_instructions": "## Plan Your Creative Artifact\r\n\r\nUse this AI chatbot to help plan and refine your final creative artifact. \r\n\r\n<br/> \r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. (Optional) Add files with any initial ideas or sketches you have created.\r\n2. Prompt AI Chat for support with your project.\r\n\r\n**Try it out!**\r\n\r\n:::details [<i class=\"fa fa-briefcase\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Need a starting prompt?**]\r\n> Should I write a script, draw a cartoon, or do something else for my final project?\r\n\r\n> How do I personify Multi-Factor Authentication in my comic strip?\r\n\r\n> Is it clear enough in my script that the user feels safer with the new user verification feature? [PASTE WRITING HERE]\r\n:::\r\n&nbsp\r\n",
